    ", 2024; Tunstall et al., 2023b) and manually select a mixture of publicly available datasets such as UltraFeedback (Cui et al., 2023), HH-RLHF (Bai et al., 2022), and TLDR-preferences (Stiennon et al., 2020a).",
    "These datasets consist of chat responses generated by a variety of LMs, and the winning/losing response is decided by prompting a judge model (e.g., or by asking human raters.",
    "We present the dataset statistics in Table 2.",
    "For more details on these datasets, please refer to Appendix A.1.",
    "Unless otherwise indicated, all dataset subsets mentioned in this section are randomly sampled from this 264K mixture."
